Class AbstractLoaderoService<T extends LoaderoModel>

  • java.lang.Object
    • loadero.service.AbstractLoaderoService<T>

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public abstract class AbstractLoaderoService<T extends LoaderoModel>
extends Object
    This abstract serves as a template for the service layer, that should be implemented for each Loadero model.
